        <div class="article-cover-content" id="main-content">
            <h1 class="hed">The Most Political Animal</h1>
            
            <p class="dek" itemprop="description">Even in one of the world’s richest countries, humans have a hard time coexisting with wolves.</p>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    
      

